     Command                Description      Reverse command
     ---------------------------------------------------------------
     ANSI_TERM_RESET        Reset settings
     ANSI_TERM_BOLD         Bold font        ANSI_TERM_BOLD_OFF
     ANSI_TERM_BRIGHT       Bright color
